cs.DS, cs.CG, cs.GT, cs.LG, cs.RO. 

The paper deals with a problem in metric spaces and proposes algorithms to solve it. This suggests that it could belong to the categories of cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.CG (Computational Geometry), and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The problem also has applications in vehicle routing, which could place it in the category of cs.RO (Robotics and Automation). Finally, the paper introduces a connection to firefighter problems on trees, which could suggest a connection to the category of cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory).
